				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Thanks, Vandaraa!<BR>
<BR>
I was lucky to have found someone to give me this information within 2-3 levels of my reaching 50 in my specialisation!  My specialisation and the primary &quot;school&quot; of magic from which it stems are now both maximised!<BR>
<BR>
It's amazing how simple this information is, yet it is overlooked by a considerable number of people.  I built my specialisation to 50, THEN put the requisite 1 point into the other four types of magicks!  Although the different magicks advance at different paces, they eventually reach 50 (and my lowest score in the regular types of magic is 189).<BR>
<BR>
It just takes patience (and someone to point out the obvious sometimes)!
